snippet.title: Dicealot - Nextfest Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon, with a now playable demo!

Dicealot is a dice-rolling roguelike with deck building elements. Easy to learn and hard to master! 

Try it now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3035330/Dicealot/
